@OffTopicJP Categories of DAO
„ÉªSocial DAO, Investment DAO, Preserver DAO, Protocol DAO, Development DAO (developing software together).
„ÉªIf you are a beginner, it is a good idea to participate in various DAOs to see the atmosphere.

@OffTopicJP Difference between a corporation and a DAO
„ÉªWhether or not it is based in a country. DAO has a strong structure to create mobility of human resources.
„ÉªThe difference is that the mobility of the hierarchy is greater in a DAO.

@OffTopicJP Web2 and Web3
„ÉªSince web3.0 is in its early stages, hybrid approaches will emerge more and more.
„ÉªHybrid approaches will continue to emerge as web 3.0 is in its early stages. Some industries will transform, while other services will continue to be centralized.
